IN RE WOODS/BRYANT, Minors. SC: 158623
COA: 345468 Supreme Court of Michigan. December 21, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the September 18, 2018 order of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the question presented should be reviewed by this Court.
